headline: Here Are Thursday’s Top Wall Street Analyst Research Calls: CAVA Group, DigitalOcean, Fox Corp, Jack Henry, Microsoft, Qualcomm, Snap, Zoom Communications, and More
summary: Pre-Market Stock Futures: Futures are trading lower once again after another up-and-down day on Wall Street. Once again, the rotation narrative rang out as software and chip stocks were hit hard, and in some cases, after posting solid fourth-quarter results.
